Installation Instructions
=========================

Required libraries:
 - python
 - python-gtk2
 - python-gtksourceview2
 - pango
 - evince
 - python-gobject
   if gio libraries is not include in python-gobject, following libraries is required:
     * gnomevfs

to install Jollpi:
==================

$ git clone https://gitlab.com/zulfian1732/jollpi2-legacy.git
$ cd jollpi2-legacy
$ chmode +x install.sh
$ ./install.sh -i

to uninstall Jollpi:
====================

$ ./install.sh -u

to run Jollpi:
==============

$ jollpi2
